{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idce278efd-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8","identifier":"/us/usc/t47/s1512"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1512"},"text":"§ 1512.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Relationship to Middle Class Tax Relief and Job Creation Act of 2012","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Nothing in this chapter shall be construed to limit, restrict, or circumvent in any way the implementation of the nationwide public safety broadband network defined in section 6001 of title VI of the Middle Class Tax Relief and Job Creation Act of 2012 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t47/s1401"},"text":"47 U.S.C. 1401","children":[],"tail":") or any rules implementing that network under title VI of that Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t47/s1401"},"text":"47 U.S.C. 1401","children":[],"tail":" et seq.)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idce278efe-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/141/dP/tVI/s622"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–141, div. P, title VI, § 622","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-03-23"},"text":"Mar. 23, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/1115"},"text":"132 Stat. 1115","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idce278eff-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idce278f00-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idce278f01-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this title”, meaning title VI of div. P of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/141"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–141","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-03-23"},"text":"Mar. 23, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/1097"},"text":"132 Stat. 1097","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of title VI to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t47/s1501"},"text":"section 1501 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Middle Class Tax Relief and Job Creation Act of 2012, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/96"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–96","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2012-02-22"},"text":"Feb. 22, 2012","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/126/156"},"text":"126 Stat. 156","children":[],"tail":". Title VI of the Act is classified principally to chapter 13 (§ 1401 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/96/s1/a"},"text":"section 1(a) of Pub. L. 112–96","children":[],"tail":", set out as a Short Title of 2012 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s1"},"text":"section 1 of Title 26","children":[],"tail":", Internal Revenue Code, and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
